insert into "products" ("body_html", "created_at", "handle", "id", "image", "images", "options", "product_type", "published_at", "published_scope", "tags", "template_suffix", "title", "metafields_global_title_tag", "metafields_global_description_tag", "updated_at", "variants", "vendor") values ('The Muddy Portable Bale Blind, with its ease of transportation, effortless set up, and ultimate concealment advantages is a great option for those hunters who don’t want to be tied down this season. These all-purpose bale blinds blend in with their surroundings by offering complete coverage under the guise of an average hay bale. A powder coated steel constructed frame offers durable stability in the field while a removable black backed water resistant denier fabric and burlap cover conceals you from the elements and the eyes of wary game. Features 8 windows for optimal shooting lane abilities, measured at 12” x 16”. All window openings secure using hooks and loops and are equipped with a removable shoot through mesh. Included is a 47” x 20” waterfowl window complete with shoot through mesh as well as ties and snaps for opening and secure closing. All window covers are reversible with black or burlap to the outside for additional concealment capabilities. Additional features include a large zippered door for easy entry, bottom wind flaps, brush ties on ends, and brush strips wrapped around 3 blind sides. Weighs 54 lbs. Dimensions: 63”L x 61”W x 76”H.Muddy Portable Bale Blind

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
